{"answer_id":"ans-gb-demo-001","question":"这个 demo 登记了哪些官方标准？","short_answer":"这个 demo 登记了 GB 7258-2017 和 GB 1589-2016 的官方 metadata，但没有保存 PDF 正文或大段标准条文。","scope":{"jurisdiction":"CN","demo_id":"gb-vehicle-safety","date":"2026-05-27"},"citations":[{"provision_id":"syn-gb7258-meta-001","source_id":"src-gb-7258-2017","locator":"metadata/status","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"},{"provision_id":"syn-gb1589-meta-001","source_id":"src-gb-1589-2016","locator":"metadata/status","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"}],"conditions":["官方 metadata 只作为 source registry 信息使用。"],"exceptions":["不包含权威标准正文。"],"version_safety":"current","confidence":"medium","unresolved_issues":["权威条款级答案需要授权 source text 和人类/BYOD review。"]}
{"answer_id":"ans-gb-demo-002","question":"这个 demo 能判断某个车辆尺寸是否符合 GB 1589 吗？","short_answer":"不能。这个 demo 只能展示 workflow 形态；真实合规答案需要车辆类别、配置、实测数值、单位，以及授权 GB 1589 文本。","scope":{"jurisdiction":"CN","document_id":"gb-1589-2016","date":"2026-05-27"},"citations":[{"provision_id":"syn-gb1589-scope-001","source_id":"src-gb-1589-2016","locator":"synthetic/scope","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"},{"provision_id":"syn-gb1589-applicability-001","source_id":"src-gb-1589-2016","locator":"synthetic/applicability","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"}],"conditions":["这是 synthetic workflow answer。"],"exceptions":["不能作为 GB 1589 pass/fail 结论。"],"version_safety":"current","confidence":"medium","unresolved_issues":["需要授权标准文本。","需要实际测量证据。"]}
{"answer_id":"ans-gb-demo-003","question":"受 GB 7258 启发的车辆安全 review 应收集哪些证据？","short_answer":"Demo 建议收集车辆身份、使用场景、检查日期、分系统安全检查结果、证据引用、reviewer notes 和 unresolved issues。","scope":{"jurisdiction":"CN","document_id":"gb-7258-2017","date":"2026-05-27"},"citations":[{"provision_id":"syn-gb7258-scope-001","source_id":"src-gb-7258-2017","locator":"synthetic/scope","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"},{"provision_id":"syn-gb7258-checks-001","source_id":"src-gb-7258-2017","locator":"synthetic/check-categories","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"},{"provision_id":"syn-gb7258-evidence-001","source_id":"src-gb-7258-2017","locator":"synthetic/evidence","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"}],"conditions":["仅作为 demo checklist 形态使用。"],"exceptions":["不是完整 GB 7258 检查清单。"],"version_safety":"current","confidence":"medium","unresolved_issues":["需要授权 GB 7258 条款后才能形成运营要求。"]}
{"answer_id":"ans-gb-demo-004","question":"PI agent 什么时候应把适用性标记为 unresolved？","short_answer":"在这个 demo 中，如果缺少车辆配置、特殊用途状态、挂车组合形式或授权来源文本，应把适用性标记为 unresolved。","scope":{"jurisdiction":"CN","demo_id":"gb-vehicle-safety","date":"2026-05-27"},"citations":[{"provision_id":"syn-gb7258-exception-001","source_id":"src-gb-7258-2017","locator":"synthetic/special-cases","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"},{"provision_id":"syn-gb1589-applicability-001","source_id":"src-gb-1589-2016","locator":"synthetic/applicability","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"}],"conditions":["适用于 demo workflow routing。"],"exceptions":["人类 reviewer 可用完整来源文本和车辆证据解决适用性问题。"],"version_safety":"current","confidence":"medium","unresolved_issues":["需要真实车辆事实。","需要授权标准文本用于最终结论。"]}
{"answer_id":"ans-gb-demo-005","question":"这个 GB demo 在公开仓库里的边界是什么？","short_answer":"公开仓库可以保存官方 metadata、locators、synthetic provisions、synthetic answers 和 coverage reports；不应保存 GB 标准 PDF 或大段标准原文。","scope":{"jurisdiction":"CN","demo_id":"gb-vehicle-safety","date":"2026-05-27"},"citations":[{"provision_id":"syn-gb7258-answer-001","source_id":"src-gb-7258-2017","locator":"synthetic/answer-contract","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"},{"provision_id":"syn-gb1589-answer-001","source_id":"src-gb-1589-2016","locator":"synthetic/answer-contract","quote_policy":"synthetic_paraphrase"}],"conditions":["公开使用 metadata-only source records。"],"exceptions":["私有/BYOD 环境可以在各自授权规则下处理授权文档。"],"version_safety":"current","confidence":"high","unresolved_issues":["仓库 license 已由 owner 选择 MIT。"]}
